kaadu &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; neram ( english : when the woods bloom ) is a 2016 indian malayalam film written and directed by dr. biju . the film is produced by sophia paul under the film production house , weekend blockbusters . it stars indrajith sukumaran as a policeman , who is sent into deep jungles to capture the chief of a radical organization , played by rima kallingal , but instead finds himself trapped in it . kaadu &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; neram premiered at the montreal world film festival in september 2016 .